      "span_text": "On the basis of their geographical distances and in considerations on their habitat continuity (relevant parameters for a commensal species with a limited dispersal capability), in a previous study the 14 sampling sites were pooled in six populations in order to assess the genetic structure of the system and the signature of hybridization between the two races using microsatellite markers [CITATION_1] ."
